data.text:
Description

A man is serenading a woman who is looking out at him from a window. He is holding a tennis racket as if it were a guitar. Text on the front: "W. S. Underwood,/Pianos, organs, sewing machines,/1 Holden St., No. Adams, Mass./Estey Organ Company/Brattleboro, VT.(U.S.A.)" Copyright 1890. Printed by J. Ottmunn Lith. Co. N.Y.
